## Technical Requirements

### CSS Variables (globals.css)
```css
:root {
  /* Background Colors */
  --bg-primary: #0A0A0A;      /* Main background */
  --bg-secondary: #141414;    /* Card/panel background */
  --bg-tertiary: #1E1E1E;     /* Elevated surfaces */
  --bg-hover: #252525;        /* Hover states */

  /* Text Colors */
  --text-primary: #FFFFFF;    /* Primary text */
  --text-secondary: #A1A1A1;  /* Secondary text */
  --text-muted: #6B6B6B;      /* Muted/disabled text */

  /* Brand Colors */
  --accent-primary: #3B82F6;  /* Primary actions (blue-500) */
  --accent-success: #22C55E;  /* Success states (green-500) */
  --accent-warning: #F59E0B;  /* Warning states (amber-500) */
  --accent-error: #EF4444;    /* Error states (red-500) */

  /* Maintenance Type Colors */
  --maint-pm1: #3B82F6;       /* PM1 - blue-500 */
  --maint-pm2: #7C3AED;       /* PM2 - violet-600 */
  --maint-hm: #F59E0B;        /* HM - amber-500 */
  --maint-ovh: #EF4444;       /* OVH - red-500 */

  /* Borders */
  --border-default: #2A2A2A;
  --border-hover: #3A3A3A;

  /* Spacing (consistent 4px grid) */
  --space-xs: 4px;
  --space-sm: 8px;
  --space-md: 16px;
  --space-lg: 24px;
  --space-xl: 32px;
  --space-2xl: 48px;

  /* Border Radius */
  --radius-sm: 4px;
  --radius-md: 8px;
  --radius-lg: 12px;
  --radius-full: 9999px;
}
```

### Tailwind Config Updates
```typescript
// tailwind.config.ts
export default {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        background: {
          primary: 'var(--bg-primary)',
          secondary: 'var(--bg-secondary)',
          tertiary: 'var(--bg-tertiary)',
          hover: 'var(--bg-hover)',
        },
        foreground: {
          primary: 'var(--text-primary)',
          secondary: 'var(--text-secondary)',
          muted: 'var(--text-muted)',
        },
        maintenance: {
          pm1: 'var(--maint-pm1)',
          pm2: 'var(--maint-pm2)',
          hm: 'var(--maint-hm)',
          ovh: 'var(--maint-ovh)',
        },
      },
    },
  },
};
```

### Migration Steps
1. Create CSS variables in globals.css
2. Update Tailwind config to reference variables
3. Search and replace hardcoded colors in components
4. Verify each page with Playwright screenshots

## Implementation Notes
- Must be completed FIRST before other Epic 8 stories
- All components should use semantic color names
- No hardcoded hex values in component files
- Creates foundation for consistent theming

